Part 2 how to build pic with Lex, Yacc and Make

pic - compile pictures for troff or TeX.
DESCRIPTION
    Each pictures starts with a line beginning with .PS
    and ends with a line beginning with .PE.
    more details on $ man pic.

dyw says that, if you want to know what a compiler is,
this is a good introduction to compiler; if you want to
know what Lex and Yacc do in details, read the Dragon Book.
